</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>†</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="You%20SC"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Seng Chan You</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Seng Chan You</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>
Department of Biomedical Informatics, Ajou University School of Medicine, Suwon, Gyeonggi-do, Republic of Korea</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="You%20SC"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Seng Chan You</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2,</sup><sup>†</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Reps%20JM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Jenna M Reps</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Jenna M Reps</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>
Janssen Research and Development, Titusville, NJ, USA</div>
