</div>
</div>
<sup>3</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Cheong%20JY"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Jae Youn Cheong</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">Jae Youn Cheong</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>
Department of Gastroenterology, Ajou University School of Medicine, Suwon, Gyeonggi-do, Republic of Korea</div>
